{"type": "article", "id": 9505, "title": "Leano 可卷曲躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-13T07:37:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235011cDRKkLym897e1pXP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t“Leano” 的名字听起来就好像在让你停下来，靠在路边休息一会儿。它是一个小毯子，又是一个小躺椅，它可以卷起来随身携带，平铺在地面上便可以让你随时随地休息，对于湖边休息，草地野餐，看星星看月亮，都是个不错的选择，支撑体采用的是实心榉木，而毯子采用的是耐磨的织物。这款作品有黄色，藏青色，绿色三种颜色可选，目前正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nikcanfly/leano-have-a-chair-everywhere\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以支持他们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235001DBTQv5ud1m7RCn2p.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350041HV3vEhlcSCzeBGs.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235007xW5J3i7MoHAamObZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350073hQoM4jC2cJdfWpk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.50488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235008OBrTxAHd0gJhj7v5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.38508557\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235008JTDE8z1qlPLQ4gxf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235009Ytj0T3UcdinE76OW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.09168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><i